SIGACT - STOC
ACM's Special Interest Groups on Algorithms and Computational Theory (SIGACT), Design Automaton (SIGDA), Management of Data (SIGMOD), and Programming Languages (SIGPLAN), the ACM SIG Projects Fund, and individual contributions.

Paris Kanellakis Theory and Practice Award
http://awards.acm.org/kanellakis/year.cfm

Eugene L. Lawler Award for Humanitarian Contributions within Computer Science and Informatics
http://awards.acm.org/lawler/year.cfm


